          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَقَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: إِنَّ رَسُولَ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "آلِهِ صَلَّى بِأَصْحَابِهِ جَالِساً فَلَمَّا فَرَغَ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:57:29",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/57/1118",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ يَؤُمَّنَّ أَحَدُكُمْ بَعْدِي جَالِساً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1118 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"The Messenger of Allah (sw) once led his companions in prayer while seated. When he finished, He (sw) said: 'None of you should lead others in prayer while seated after me.'\"."
        ]
      }
    },
